list_page_teaser: No family would be complete without cousins.  Facebook helps some of us keep in touch.  Click to learn more!
description_html:
This gallery contains the spiritual portraits of some of my cousins.

They are spread out around the country but some of us keep in touch on Facebook.
story_html:
I am in the process of contacting more cousins and adding their portraits to this gallery.

To learn when I add new images, follow this site on social media or join the SeeOurMinds.com email list!

image_list.title: Lin C.
image_list.subtitle_html: Works for NASA
image_list.gallery_page_teaser: Lin is a cousin on my father's side.  She works for NASA.  Click on the image to learn more!
image_list.explain_dom: The Yellow in this spiritual portrait represents Lin's dominant trait, her pragmatism.  In Introverts, the dominant trait is directed inwardly, and spiritual portraits use a long horizontal line to represent this.
image_list.explain_aux: The Green in this spiritual portrait represents Lin's auxiliary trait, her rationality.  In Introverts, the auxiliary trait is directed outwardly, and spiritual portraits use a vertical line to represent this, because it is more evident than the dominant function.
image_list.story_intro_html: Lin lives in Hampton, Virginia with her husband Henry. Their daughter is a graduate of ....
image_list.story_html:
Lin lives in Hampton, Virginia with her husband Henry. Their daughter is a graduate of Yale University and now works as a Research and Instrument Analyst at the Space Telescope Science Institute.

I will share more information as it becomes available.

image_list.subtitle_html: Technical Manager at Air National Guard Recruiting

image_list.explain_aux: The Green in this spiritual portrait represents Oren's auxiliary trait, his rationality.  In Introverts, the auxiliary trait is directed outwardly, and spiritual portraits use a vertical line to represent this, because it is more evident than the dominant function.
image_list.story_intro_html: Oren lives in Milwaukie, Oregon. He has a Bachelor of Science in Industrial/Organizational Psychology from ....
image_list.story_html:
Oren lives in Milwaukie, Oregon. He has a Bachelor of Science in Industrial/Organizational Psychology from Christopher Newport University and a Master's degree from Lutheran Theological Southern Seminary.

I will share more information as it becomes available.

image_list.title: Richard H.
image_list.subtitle_html: Retired President of Time Out Sports Cafe
image_list.gallery_page_teaser: Richard H is a cousin on my father's side.  Having worked in the restarant business for many years, he is experienced with all aspects of it.  Click on the image to learn more!
image_list.explain_dom: The Red in this spiritual portrait represents Richard's dominant trait, a moderate preference for using emotion for making decisions.  In Introverts, the dominant trait is directed inwardly, and spiritual portraits use a long horizontal line to represent this.  He demonstrates this in his love of music.
image_list.explain_aux: The Blue in this spiritual portrait represents Richard's auxiliary trait, a moderate preference for perceiving ideas rather than facts.  In Introverts, the auxiliary trait is directed outwardly, and spiritual portraits use a vertical line to represent this, because it is more evident than the dominant function.  He demonstrates this in the way he encourages his friends to show more tolerance toward others and overlook relatively minor negative traits.
image_list.story_intro_html: Richard lives in Pearl, Mississippi. He went to college at ...
image_list.story_html:
Richard lives in Pearl, Mississippi. He went to college at Hinds Community College and now goes to St. Marks United Methodist Church in Brandon Mississippi.

I will share more information as it becomes available.

image_list.title: Debbie H.
image_list.gallery_page_teaser: Debbie's spiritual portrait is similar to Richard's, but shows more Extraversion and emotion (Red).  They are no longer married but still close.  Click on the image to learn more!
image_list.explain_dom: The Red in this spiritual portrait represents Debbie's dominant trait, her warmth and compassion.  In Extraverts, the dominant trait is directed outwardly, and spiritual portraits use a long vertical line to represent this, because it is the side of their personality that is most evident.
image_list.explain_aux: The Blue in this spiritual portrait represents Debbie's auxiliary trait, her iNtuition.  In Extraverts, the auxiliary trait is directed inwardly, and spiritual portraits use a horizontal line to represent this.
image_list.story_intro_html: Debbie lives in Flowood, Mississippi. She has a degree from The University of ....
image_list.story_html:
Debbie lives in Flowood, Mississippi. She has a degree from The University of Southern Mississippi.

I will share more information as it becomes available.
